                                    No parts found for &ldquo;<strong id="parts-no-results-term"></strong>&rdquo;
                                </p>
                                <button
                                    onclick="document.getElementById('parts-search-input').value=''; filterParts();"
                                    style="background:none; border:1.5px solid #c5d3e8; border-radius:6px;
                                           padding:6px 18px; font-size:0.85rem; color:#1a73e8; cursor:pointer;">
                                    Clear search
                                </button>
                            </div>

                            </div>
